# CODEOWNERS for csa-inabox
# Each line: pattern  @owner1 @owner2
# Last matching pattern wins.
#
# Today every line routes to @fgarofalo56 because the repo is currently
# single-maintainer. To onboard a second maintainer:
#   1. Read docs/SUCCESSION.md for the criteria and onboarding flow.
#   2. Add the new GitHub handle to the lines below (e.g. add a second
#      @handle separated by a space — last matching pattern wins, so the
#      override granularity is preserved).
#   3. Once the second maintainer is active, enable required PR reviews
#      on the main branch via repo settings → branches → main (or the
#      `gh api PATCH .../branches/main/protection` command in
#      docs/SUCCESSION.md).

# Default — every PR pings the repo owner unless overridden below.

